    <string name="footer_text_part_1">Made with\u0020</string>
    <string name="footer_text_part_2">\u0020by a cookie monster.</string>
    <string name="about_content_paragraph_1">Cookies. They come in all varieties: butter cookies,
        chocolate chip, Graham crackers, saltine crackers, digestive, with raisins, gingerbread&#8230;
        \u0020the imagination is the limit!</string>
    <string name="about_content_paragraph_2">As a child I looked forward to the weekly bake at home,
        in which the house filled with the sweetest scents. I enjoyed gradually going from measuring
        the dry ingredients to eventually baking my own batches of cookies.</string>
    <string name="about_content_paragraph_3">Cookies and milk made doing tedious homework a more
        pleasurable task. Alone as a snack or as part of an appetizer, cookies are meant to be
        enjoyed to the fullest.</string>
    <string name="about_content_paragraph_4">Cookie Jar is born out of the wish to keep the child
        inside alive. All the cookies are personally vetted to provide the highest quality possible
        at affordable prices. </string>
